# Pereste brand assets
#
# Static logos:
#   logo-primary.png     full lockup (mark + PERESTE) — black on transparent (default)
#   logo-black.png       full lockup, pure black variant
#   logo-white.png       full lockup, white — for use on dark backgrounds
#   logo-inverse.png     full lockup, lavender — for use on white
#   mark-square.png      mark inside rounded square on lavender (used in header)
#   brandkit-circle.png  mark inside circle on lavender (alternate)
#
# Animated SVGs (not loaded by default — heavy):
#   anim-intro.svg       wipe-in entrance
#   anim-loop.svg        looping idle
#   anim-outro.svg       sweep exit
